
# Lyyli.io Brand Guidelines

## Brand Overview
**Mission**: Lyyli.io empowers solo entrepreneurs, micro-businesses, and small teams to communicate effectively across all platforms through an AI assistant that feels human, trustworthy, and approachable.

**Core Values**: Empathy, Reliability, Discreet Intelligence, Clarity, Accessibility

**Brand Personality**: Friendly and approachable, Calm and reassuring, Encouraging, Practical, Thoughtful, Humble

